items.title: California fires live updates: Biden to give remarks on fire response
items.description: At least five people are dead and many more injured as several fires broke out across Southern California amid historically dry and windy conditions.

items.title: Before, during and after the wildfires: A look at the devastation in California

items.title: Trump talks with Barack Obama, shakes hands with Mike Pence during Carter funeral
items.description: Donald Trump shook hands with Mike Pence at Jimmy Carter's state funeral -- a notable exchange as the two men have not interacted publicly in years.
